phpfoxLABS - MegaPoke phpFox Module Instillation Guide

MegaPoke 1.0 Features:
- Unlimited Poke Types
- Feed and Notification Support
- Email Notification
- All Phrases in Phrase Manager
- User Group settings for "Posting to Feed" and to "Disable MegaPoke"
- User Privacy Settings to turn off MegaPoking on profile.
- User Notification Settings to stop getting Poke Notification Emails
- Flood Control to stop over MegaPoking 

No Core Modifications: Just upload, install in Admin CP, add Poke Types, and start poking!

